PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated on:
June 25, 2024
Prior version effective on:
January 2023
PRIVACY POLICY INTRODUCTION
The Finish Line, Inc. d/b/a Finish Line and JD Sports (referred to as “
JD Finish Line
,” “
we
,” “
us
,” or “
our
” in this Privacy Policy) operates the retail brands of Finish Line and JD Sports or JD (“
Brands
”) in the U.S. and certain U.S. Territories. We take seriously the trust you place in us when you choose to do business with us.
The purpose of our privacy policy (this “
Privacy Policy
”) is to inform you about the types of Personal Information we gather about you, how we may use that information, whether we disclose it to anyone and the rights and choices you have regarding that information.
“
Personal Information
” means any information from which you can be identified or are identifiable, either directly or indirectly, such as your name, address, telephone number, device and browsing information, etc.
If you want the best products and services JD Finish Line offers, we need certain Personal Information of yours. We use your Personal Information to provide you our products and services, communicate with you, market products and services that may be of interest to you and secure our operations.
By using our Services, you agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, which is part of our
Terms of Use
, and you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your Personal Information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please discontinue use of our Services immediately. By accessing and continuing to use our Services, you agree to the collection and use of Personal Information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
Our Privacy Policy applies to Personal Information  that may be collected by or for us through our “
Services
”, namely:
in our Finish Line and JD Sports retail stores and Finish Line shops located in Macy’s stores (collectively, “
Stores
”);
online at finishline.com and jdsports.com and at our blogs at blog.finishline.com and blog.jdsports.com (collectively, “
Site
”);
when you purchase products offered by Finish Line through macys.com;
through our Finish Line and JD Sports mobile application(s) (“
App
”);
in connection with our JD Finish Line brand loyalty membership program known as STATUS (“
Loyalty Program
”);
for our sweepstakes, contests and surveys;
through our registration and event services;
by Store associates, JD Sports Customer Care representatives and Finish Line Customer Care representatives; and
by and through emails, social media or other digital platforms, including our digital ads which may be delivered on third-party websites (collectively, “
Internet Marketing Platforms
”).
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.
