PERSONAL INFORMATION WE COLLECT
Sensitive Personal Information
In some circumstances, when you grant us permission to do so, JD Finish Line collects, uses, and processes Personal Information, which is classified as sensitive information under applicable data protection and privacy laws.
Categories of sensitive Personal Information we collect with your permission include the following:
Precise geolocation information (in relation to your use of the App)
Personal Information
We collect various types of Personal Information about and related to you. In general, we collect and store such Personal Information either directly (for example, when you create a customer account) or automatically (for example, when you visit our Site) from you.
Personal Information we collect includes:
DATA CATEGORY
EXAMPLES OF SPECIFIC DATA
Analytics Information
Customer Profile
Purchasing Tendencies
Transaction Tendencies
Automatically Collected
Personal Information
Technical information
IP (internet protocol) address, the type of browser, device or hardware you are using, including device model, operating system version, unique device identifiers and mobile network information.
Your interactions with certain Services
How you use our Site, App and Internet Marketing Platforms, including the time you spend on these Services, the way you navigate through these Services and search terms you enter when using these Services.
Your interactions with the ads we serve
Interaction with our content presented on a third-party website or mobile application.
Your geolocation,
including the precise location of your device
Browsing Information
Browsing time
Cookie information
Device identifier
Network interaction history
Site history
