How Long We Keep Your Personal Information
JD Finish Line uses several criteria to determine how long we should keep categories of Personal Information. We generally keep Personal Information until we no longer have a business purpose for the data or until we no longer have an obligation to keep it. Please understand that residual copies of the Personal Information can be stored in locations or formats that make complete erasure extremely difficult.
The best way to ensure you control your Personal Information is to give us only the Personal Information that you are completely comfortable sharing with us.
HOW WE DISCLOSE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION
As outlined below, we disclose your Personal Information to third parties. Additionally, we disclose your Personal Information to our affiliates, including any parent or subsidiary entity, for marketing or advertising purposes.
Selling to Third Parties
JD Finish Line has not sold your Personal Information nor do we have knowledge of sales of Personal Information of individuals under the age of 16. What we mean by ‘selling’ is disclosing your Personal Information to a third party as part of a monetary exchange.
Sharing with Third Parties
JD Finish Line shares Personal Information. What we mean by ‘sharing’ is disclosing Personal Information to a third party for the purpose of cross-site behavioral or targeted advertising.
We share browsing information, analytics information, precise geolocation and Automatically Collected Personal Information with social media platforms, advertising partners, and analytics platform partners like Google.
With social media platforms
, such as Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Pinterest, TikTok, and Instagram through social media widgets and other tools used in connection with our Site and App. Some of these third parties use your Personal Information collected through your use of our Site to deliver the third party’s own services and target ads on their sites and mobile applications.
With promotional partners
, we partner with similar businesses and brands who we may enable to collect information through our Services to offer you shared promotions programs. Each loyalty program will be subject to terms provided to you when you register your loyalty program account.
With Nike.
Loyalty program (STATUS) Members can connect their account with their Nike Membership account to become eligible for exclusive benefits. By connecting your STATUS Account and Nike Membership Accounts, JD Finish Line shares with Nike information about in-store and online Nike-related purchases and transactions. You can unlink your accounts at any time.
With advertising partners,
who deliver cross-site, target ads both on our platform and on third-party sites and apps.
With analytics services
, such as Google Analytics.
