LIMITING OUR COLLECTION AND USE OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION
We offer you choices about how we collect and use Personal Information relating to you. Please be aware that disallowing certain data collection may limit the usefulness of our Services, including our Site and App and across our Brands. Your choices include the following:
Postal Mail, Text Messages and Emails
From time to time, we communicate with you for marketing and promotional purposes through postal mail, emails and text messages. We will only send you marketing or promotional communications where you elect to receive them, and you may revoke your consent to receive such marketing or promotional communications at any time by following the instructions below or otherwise provided. Opting in to receiving marketing or promotional communications from us is optional and is not a condition for purchase.
Even if you opt-out of receiving marketing or promotional communications from us, we may still contact you to respond to an inquiry and for transactional purposes (for example, sales confirmations, order fulfillment or shipping notifications).
Postal Mail.
To opt-out of receiving catalogs, coupons and other promotional postal mail, you may contact our
JD Customer Care Team
and our
Finish Line Customer Care Team
.
A Customer Care representative will be happy to assist you. Please allow a reasonable period of time for your request to be removed from our promotional mailing contact list to be made effective.
Emails (Opt-In).
You will have the option to opt-in to receiving marketing and promotional emails from us (which may include emails from the Brands). You can opt-in to receiving promotional emails on jdsports.com and finishline.com through your “Profile” under “My Account”; when you opt-in, you are providing your prior express written consent to receive recurring marketing and promotional and support emails from us. These may include cart abandon messages. Message frequency varies. We will not be liable for any delays in the receipt of, or failure to deliver, any emails, as delivery is subject to effective transmission from your network operator. Email services are provided on an “AS IS” basis.
Emails (Opt-Out).
To opt-out of receiving marketing and promotional emails from us and to unsubscribe from future marketing and promotional emails, you may
u
se the “Unsubscribe Link” included within a promotional email from us to you or change your preferences in your “Profile” under “My Account” which you can access on jdsports.com and finishline.com. We will process your opt-out as soon as possible and within the timeframe required by applicable law.
Text Messages (Opt-In).
You will have the option to opt-in to receiving marketing and promotional text messages from us. You can opt-in to receiving promotional text messages either via jdsports.com and finishline.com or by sending a text message indicating your opt-in election; when you opt-in, you are providing your prior express written consent to receive recurring marketing and promotional and support text messages from us sent through an automatic telephone dialing system. These may include cart abandon messages. Message frequency varies. In addition to any fee of which you are notified, your mobile provider’s message and data rates may apply to text messages you have opted-in to receive from us (including our text message confirming your opt-in and all subsequent text messages). Under no circumstances will we be responsible for any text messaging or wireless charges incurred by you or by a person who has access to your wireless device or telephone number. If your carrier does not permit text messages, you may not receive text messages from us. We will not be liable for any delays in the receipt of, or failure to deliver, any text messages, as delivery is subject to effective transmission from your network operator. For help, follow the help instructions provided in our text message (for example, by replying “HELP” to any text message you receive from us). Text message services are provided on an “AS IS” basis.
Text Messages (Opt-Out).
To opt-out of receiving promotional text messages from us, follow the opt-out instructions provided in our text message (for example, by replying “STOP” to any text message you receive from us). You will no longer receive text messages from the applicable text list, but you may receive text messages if you are subscribed to other text lists and have not unsubscribed from those lists. We will process your opt-out as soon as possible and within the timeframe required by applicable law.
Loyalty Program
.
